Package: bittorrent
Description-md5: 9fd3856934c4d458797a50df8ef35203
Description-de: Originales BitTorrent-Programm und -Tracker – Konsolenwerkzeuge
 BitTorrent is a tool for distributing files. It's extremely easy to use -
 downloads are started by clicking on hyperlinks. Whenever more than one
 person is downloading at once they send pieces of the file(s) to each
